s/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8094bc809dfb85b48dac416321cb34a85c2a0126","tid":179024,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同性就無問題</blockquote><br />\n成班男人會去叫雞點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我信我男朋友唔會做呢啲野 同埋 佢會玩得埋既朋友一定都唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男朋友仔我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同另一半都唔會想自己去旅行<br />\n其實唔知可以果d到底係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好簡單啫，同另一半去旅行好開心，同朋友去又係另一種樂趣，有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n唔是覺得有問題<br />\n但係我唔會囉 點解唔可以一齊去？"},{"pid":"4a7159abd9d852a93077c9bdd0998ad9b6bcd683","tid":179024,"uid":48460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"469d89c79c33dd997bfb3ad8a2d638e2ab450aa9","tid":179024,"uid":72967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:32:15.000Z","msg":"比呀 最後出左事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個晚飲醉酒 之後就..............<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fea837022f91d6d2ea8944e2450be8bf6921d3","tid":179024,"uid":39866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同性就無問題</blockquote><br />\n成班男人會去叫雞點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我信我男朋友唔會做呢啲野 同埋 佢會玩得埋既朋友一定都唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男朋友仔我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同另一半都唔會想自己去旅行<br />\n其實唔知可以果d到底係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好簡單啫，同另一半去旅行好開心，同朋友去又係另一種樂趣，有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n唔是覺得有問題<br />\n但係我唔會囉 點解唔可以一齊去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你去又要照顧埋你一份<br />\n唔通佢丟低你自己同朋友吹水咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec8460d238ae1a47628c04f6f486da953c5ec69","tid":179024,"uid":80954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:48:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同性就無問題</blockquote><br />\n成班男人會去叫雞點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我信我男朋友唔會做呢啲野 同埋 佢會玩得埋既朋友一定都唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男朋友仔我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同另一半都唔會想自己去旅行<br />\n其實唔知可以果d到底係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好簡單啫，同另一半去旅行好開心，同朋友去又係另一種樂趣，有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n唔是覺得有問題<br />\n但係我唔會囉 點解唔可以一齊去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點解唔可以同朋友一齊去？旅行唔係一定要同另一半去架啵~<br />\n況且如果夾唔到假 / 去嘅地點對方無興趣 / 對方唔想洗錢去旅行，咁咪同朋友去囉~我自己就無乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n利申：極少去旅行，另一半去得唔多但多過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28264b6930ee5e0d976eb2df25dd1baface5489","tid":179024,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:50:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比呀 最後出左事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個晚飲醉酒 之後就..............<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c5839b52b5c7f6e0af756eaac4632e36683d25e","tid":179024,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同性就無問題</blockquote><br />\n成班男人會去叫雞點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我信我男朋友唔會做呢啲野 同埋 佢會玩得埋既朋友一定都唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男朋友仔我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同另一半都唔會想自己去旅行<br />\n其實唔知可以果d到底係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好簡單啫，同另一半去旅行好開心，同朋友去又係另一種樂趣，有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n唔是覺得有問題<br />\n但係我唔會囉 點解唔可以一齊去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你去又要照顧埋你一份<br />\n唔通佢丟低你自己同朋友吹水咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢朋友又唔係我朋友  佢地傾男人野你又要係到得住哂顧住你 邊玩得開心  同埋男人聚埋一齊都唔一定係嫖賭蕩既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e313249eb52871a8e59c3f833a2766e81ba9944b","tid":179024,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同性就無問題</blockquote><br />\n成班男人會去叫雞點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我信我男朋友唔會做呢啲野 同埋 佢會玩得埋既朋友一定都唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男朋友仔我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同另一半都唔會想自己去旅行<br />\n其實唔知可以果d到底係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好簡單啫，同另一半去旅行好開心，同朋友去又係另一種樂趣，有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n唔是覺得有問題<br />\n但係我唔會囉 點解唔可以一齊去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點解唔可以同朋友一齊去？旅行唔係一定要同另一半去架啵~<br />\n況且如果夾唔到假 / 去嘅地點對方無興趣 / 對方唔想洗錢去旅行，咁咪同朋友去囉~我自己就無乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n利申：極少去旅行，另一半去得唔多但多過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁時間金錢<br />\n都係夾架姐 要夾 肯夾點會夾唔到<br />\n另一半嚟架wo"},{"pid":"163c2b7cdad19c306c5a380681bd9117dd9531b6","tid":179024,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T03:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n成班男人會去叫雞點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我信我男朋友唔會做呢啲野 同埋 佢會玩得埋既朋友一定都唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男朋友仔我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同另一半都唔會想自己去旅行<br />\n其實唔知可以果d到底係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好簡單啫，同另一半去旅行好開心，同朋友去又係另一種樂趣，有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n唔是覺得有問題<br />\n但係我唔會囉 點解唔可以一齊去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你去又要照顧埋你一份<br />\n唔通佢丟低你自己同朋友吹水咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢朋友又唔係我朋友  佢地傾男人野你又要係到得住哂顧住你 邊玩得開心  同埋男人聚埋一齊都唔一定係嫖賭蕩既姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔會想留低佢一個喺香港<br />\n我自己去左同其他人開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔捨得"},{"pid":"f9196bf9452830f29703fa37bbe8868e6eb68ce2","tid":179024,"uid":80954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:09:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同性就無問題</blockquote><br />\n成班男人會去叫雞點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我信我男朋友唔會做呢啲野 同埋 佢會玩得埋既朋友一定都唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n男朋友仔我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同另一半都唔會想自己去旅行<br />\n其實唔知可以果d到底係咩心態</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好簡單啫，同另一半去旅行好開心，同朋友去又係另一種樂趣，有咩問題</blockquote><br />\n唔是覺得有問題<br />\n但係我唔會囉 點解唔可以一齊去？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁點解唔可以同朋友一齊去？旅行唔係一定要同另一半去架啵~<br />\n況且如果夾唔到假 / 去嘅地點對方無興趣 / 對方唔想洗錢去旅行，咁咪同朋友去囉~我自己就無乜所謂<br />\n<br />\n利申：極少去旅行，另一半去得唔多但多過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁時間金錢<br />\n都係夾架姐 要夾 肯夾點會夾唔到<br />\n另一半嚟架wo</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我比較無所謂又比較怕麻煩，有時覺得拍拖唔代表唔可以cost-effective（e.g.平日都唔俾佢送我番屋企，覺得好費時失事），佢同朋友夾到咪同朋友去囉，最緊要佢開心~我留喺香港等睇佢旅行相聽佢旅行趣事都好好~"},{"pid":"c87aa0ff97285b4f31a269ff87fa83600ef591c7","tid":179024,"uid":13897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:11:36.000Z","msg":"咁大個人有得唔比架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1191245241b2899f7586773ea11036ea6b8b8cc","tid":179024,"uid":72739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁大個人有得唔比架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔想姐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}